{"tid":2252242,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"街貓病咗","createTime":"2020-10-21T10:47:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T12:18:12.000Z","uid":78418,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4a4af0e3af3b156203755def48cb1b91f1f33740","tid":2252242,"uid":78418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T10:47:50.000Z","msg":"平時係附近有人餵開<br />\n我行過都有摸吓佢同餵吓零食<br />\n雖然佢唔係好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最近發現佢突然暴瘦<br />\n<br />\n點解話佢暴瘦<br />\n係因為之前摸佢都正常<br />\n但係啱啱摸完佢<br />\n就發現佢脊骨去到盆骨嗰個位<br />\n瘦到啲骨凸咗出嚟<br />\n想問下有冇義工可以幫手帶佢睇醫生？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢已絕育同佢好親人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y6tYhQP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY6tYhQP.png&h=d06201b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我未有能力可以帶佢睇醫生<br />\n因為前排自己嘅貓貓病咗用咗好多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望有心人幫幫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"009d0712c927b3db48bf653eede1bebdfcddfcd1","tid":2252242,"uid":78418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T12:13:40.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c9bd05b9f56b6c3b268a28c279275c39bcdd3a2","tid":2252242,"uid":79589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T12:14:32.000Z","msg":"咩地方？<br />\n捉到佢入籠？"},{"pid":"6745f247a3b42473e52ea842f5ab70e98c0555ca","tid":2252242,"uid":78418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c9bd05b9f56b6c3b268a28c279275c39bcdd3a2","tid":2252242,"uid":79589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T12:14:32.000Z","msg":"咩地方？<br />\n捉到佢入籠？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T12:23:21.000Z","msg"